name: Cyber Sea Creatures - Seeker
description: A fusion of alien technology and a gigantic stingray species from the plant Xidu. Seeker is the ultimate hunter, sent on countless search and destroy missions, he always finds his target and finishes the job. Obsessive personality,seems to have ADHD and a bit prickly until you get to know him. Gigawatt shock tail, explosive seeker mine orbs, and plasma cutting pectoral fins.
